                <![CDATA[<p>以前講到電競手提電腦，都是「大牛龜」又厚又重，而且風扇聲超級嘈吵。不過在剛剛的 CES 2025 亮相的全新 ROG Flow Z13 (2025) ，薄到像一部平板電腦一樣（事實上它可拆除鍵盤，變身平板電腦），可説是市場上少數兼具高效能與二合一靈活性的電競裝置。而這部手提電腦在外觀設計上都展現獨特風格，硬體規格也讓人驚豔，今次小編就借到這部新機，同大家睇睇這部真正可以輕便帶出街玩的電競手提電腦。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294109" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05045-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05045-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05045.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294110" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05068-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05068-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05068.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>外觀設計與機身結構</h2><p>ROG Flow Z13 (2025) 採用堅固的金屬材質機身，部分 CNC 切割工藝確保裝置的耐用度。背面搭載 RGB 燈效視窗，光線透過金屬切割縫隙散發，營造極具科技感的氛圍，別具有 ROG 產品風格。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294124" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05045-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05045-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05045-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294122" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05038-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05038-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05038.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294123" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05036-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05036-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05036.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>這部手提電腦作為電競機，重量只約 1.2 kg，雖然相較於其他 2 合 1 平板稍微厚重，但考慮到高階硬體配置還有散熱系統，這樣的重量仍在可接受範圍內。機身背部配備 1300 萬像素後置鏡頭與 500 萬像素前置鏡頭，方便視訊會議或文件掃描。</p><h2>操作方式與使用體驗</h2><p>ROG Flow Z13 延續 2 合 1 設計，搭載可拆卸鍵盤，使用者可自由切換手提電腦與平板模式。這個鍵盤是另一個小編十分喜歡的地方，它雖未採用機械軸設計，但鍵程適中且回饋感良好，觸控板則具備玻璃材質與震動回饋機制，操控手感優異，考慮到它是可拆除設計，質感同觸感都令人滿足。鍵盤 RGB 燈效可作為附加的襯託。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294116" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05069-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05069-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05069.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294117" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05049-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05049-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05049.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲背面以及鍵盤的 RGB 燈效</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294118" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05055-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05055-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05055.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可以拆卸的鍵盤</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294119" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05056-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05056-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05056.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲拆除後電腦便變成平板電腦，支援觸控操作</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294120" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05060-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05060-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05060.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用手指或觸控筆都可操作電腦</p><p>ROG Flow Z13 隨附 ASUS Pen 觸控筆，提供更直覺的輸入方式，適合繪圖、筆記或簽名用途。雖然鍵盤僅能透過物理連接使用，未提供藍牙無線模式，但小編反而喜歡這種較實在的連接方法，重點是隻要輕易磁吸上去就可用到，整體使用體驗流暢。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294134" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05047-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05047-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05047.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294135" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05054-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05054-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05054.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲作為一部二合一電腦，它的鍵盤當然可攤開到 180 度也可拆除</p><p>這部電腦的螢幕為 13 吋 Quad HD IPS 面板，更新率高達 180Hz，反應時間為 3ms，確保遊戲畫面流暢穩定。亮度方面最高達 500 尼特，雖不及 OLED，但考量到成本與續航力，此選擇仍屬合理。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294121" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05043-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05043-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05043.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>
